<h4 style="text-align: center;">           AIMS Mission Statement</h4>

Albuquerque Institute for Mathematics and Science @ UNM (AIMS@UNM) is committed to preparing its students, grades six thru twelve, for college, community, and beyond through a rigorous focus on math and science and an emphasis on global participation. 

